summary:
Hi, I’m Alex — a creative media nerd who likes to play with words and concepts.

My passion? Achieving the unachievable with integrity, an open mind and a solid rationale.

I’m big on semantics, always up for a challenge and very much into philosophy, psychology and business. Oh, and writing. And film. And a bunch of other stuff. Learning things is actually kind of a hobby. 

When it comes to copy, I have fun simplifying even the most complex message — making it interesting, approachable and fine tuned to the smallest detail.
